WEBVTT


00:00:48.240 --> 00:00:52.920
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

00:00:53.400 --> 00:00:56.030
[Episode 17]

00:01:08.350 --> 00:01:09.840
When boundaries blur,

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:12.230
people are especially likely

00:01:12.230 --> 00:01:14.000
to mistake virtual projections

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:15.130
for reality itself.

00:01:16.840 --> 00:01:19.000
But programs have no real memories,

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:22.440
only predetermined
arrivals and departures.

00:01:23.789 --> 00:01:26.120
When reality is nothing more than an echo,

00:01:26.789 --> 00:01:28.350
the hotter the love burns,

00:01:28.950 --> 00:01:30.950
the colder the hatred becomes.

00:01:33.039 --> 00:01:35.150
It is we ourselves who trap ourselves

00:01:36.229 --> 00:01:39.640
in true suffering.

00:02:05.950 --> 00:02:06.480
Who is it?

00:02:15.280 --> 00:02:16.079
Are you crazy?

00:02:17.910 --> 00:02:18.870
What are you doing there?

00:02:18.870 --> 00:02:20.150
This is the 17th floor.

00:02:20.240 --> 00:02:22.300
Didn't you like me playing the thief?

00:02:24.150 --> 00:02:26.120
These are Yuanji's clothes in the game.

00:02:26.120 --> 00:02:27.590
Why are you dressed like this?

00:02:27.590 --> 00:02:29.079
These are starter clothes.

00:02:29.079 --> 00:02:31.540
Every character has them
in their wardrobe.

00:02:31.710 --> 00:02:33.120
I thought you'd like it.

00:02:33.630 --> 00:02:34.590
Psycho.

00:02:44.960 --> 00:02:46.020
What are you doing?

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:47.660
None of your business.

00:02:49.310 --> 00:02:50.400
Your eyes...

00:02:54.150 --> 00:02:55.960
Aren't your eyes green?

00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:58.400
Why are they black now?

00:02:58.630 --> 00:03:00.080
I applied to the system

00:03:00.280 --> 00:03:01.710
to change my eye color.

00:03:02.150 --> 00:03:03.860
I could buy a color-change pack,

00:03:03.860 --> 00:03:05.540
but it only lasts one day.

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:07.800
This is the color of Yuanji's eyes.

00:03:07.800 --> 00:03:08.590
Can you tell?

00:03:08.960 --> 00:03:10.310
What exactly do you want?

00:03:10.310 --> 00:03:11.560
To make you like me.

00:03:19.079 --> 00:03:20.880
If you can change your eye color,

00:03:20.960 --> 00:03:21.710
why don't you change your face

00:03:21.710 --> 00:03:22.910
to Yuanji's too?

00:03:23.190 --> 00:03:24.390
It's not that I can't,

00:03:24.470 --> 00:03:26.670
but I don't get picked often in the game,

00:03:26.960 --> 00:03:28.470
so I don't have enough gold coins.

00:03:28.470 --> 00:03:29.750
One color-change pack

00:03:29.910 --> 00:03:31.370
cost me almost all of them.

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:32.490
Changing my face

00:03:32.560 --> 00:03:33.890
would be too expensive.

00:03:35.560 --> 00:03:36.079
I!

00:03:36.910 --> 00:03:38.280
Won't top up for you!

00:03:38.630 --> 00:03:39.560
No need.

00:03:41.240 --> 00:03:42.470
I brought you a gift.

00:03:51.520 --> 00:03:52.910
It's a new online feature,

00:03:52.910 --> 00:03:53.680
allowing me to buy clothes,

00:03:53.680 --> 00:03:54.680
jewelry and stuff

00:03:54.710 --> 00:03:55.680
for you, Princess.

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:57.840
You always wear so little.

00:03:58.280 --> 00:03:59.680
I wanted to buy you a coat,

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:01.570
but I didn't have enough money.

00:04:29.630 --> 00:04:32.360
The bundle is really useful.

00:05:01.720 --> 00:05:02.520
What's wrong?

00:05:02.830 --> 00:05:03.760
Are you unhappy?

00:05:06.950 --> 00:05:07.630
I'm sorry.

00:05:08.310 --> 00:05:09.840
Should I not have done that?

00:05:10.510 --> 00:05:12.000
You did great.

00:05:13.430 --> 00:05:14.310
But...

00:05:15.800 --> 00:05:16.720
Thank you.

00:05:19.310 --> 00:05:20.480
You are not Yuanji.

00:05:23.310 --> 00:05:24.190
Leave now.

00:05:34.870 --> 00:05:35.560
Yesterday,

00:05:35.950 --> 00:05:37.800
you said you didn't like Yuanji anymore

00:05:37.800 --> 00:05:39.060
and that you hated him.

00:05:40.159 --> 00:05:41.430
I searched the system

00:05:42.480 --> 00:05:43.810
to find out what hate is.

00:05:45.270 --> 00:05:46.670
I came across a sentence:

00:05:47.480 --> 00:05:49.510
"The opposite of love is hate.

00:05:50.830 --> 00:05:52.290
The more you love someone,

00:05:53.159 --> 00:05:54.490
the more you hate them."

00:05:57.560 --> 00:05:59.720
I didn't understand this sentence.

00:06:01.800 --> 00:06:03.190
Now I do.

00:06:05.040 --> 00:06:06.680
Did the system

00:06:07.390 --> 00:06:07.950
ever say

00:06:08.950 --> 00:06:09.800
what love is?

00:06:11.270 --> 00:06:12.360
I don't know.

00:06:56.560 --> 00:06:57.870
Hey, honey.

00:06:58.310 --> 00:06:59.240
Long time no see.

00:07:00.480 --> 00:07:02.240
I have some revelations to make.

00:07:02.240 --> 00:07:03.870
I'm going to release some content.

00:07:03.870 --> 00:07:05.680
I've already sorted everything out.

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:07.390
Do you have any channels to get this out?

00:07:07.390 --> 00:07:09.190
I don't have a promotion budget.

00:07:10.070 --> 00:07:10.950
But...

00:07:11.750 --> 00:07:13.410
I'm Yuanji's ex-girlfriend.

00:07:13.630 --> 00:07:15.490
I've got lots of intimate photos,

00:07:15.560 --> 00:07:16.690
even bedroom shots.

00:07:17.190 --> 00:07:18.650
Is that explosive enough?

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:24.250
Have you all seen it?

00:07:24.560 --> 00:07:26.420
It's going viral on the internet.

00:07:26.720 --> 00:07:27.360
Wang Fang and that idol guy's

00:07:27.360 --> 00:07:28.330
bedroom photos.

00:07:28.490 --> 00:07:29.560
They are insane!

00:07:30.190 --> 00:07:30.870
Yuanji?

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:33.720
Even a 2D idol has a girlfriend?

00:07:33.720 --> 00:07:34.720
Who's the leaker?

00:07:35.510 --> 00:07:36.750
Someone under a fake account.

00:07:36.750 --> 00:07:38.390
Lots of other accounts are pushing it too.

00:07:38.390 --> 00:07:39.590
It's definitely her.

00:07:39.920 --> 00:07:41.070
Who else could have

00:07:41.159 --> 00:07:42.420
such intimate photos?

00:07:42.950 --> 00:07:45.040
I remember they were together before.

00:07:45.040 --> 00:07:45.750
Didn't they

00:07:45.920 --> 00:07:46.920
kiss that time?

00:07:46.950 --> 00:07:47.560
Yes, yes.

00:07:54.390 --> 00:07:55.720
Hello, this is Xinghuo.

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:57.159
Wang Fang?

00:07:57.950 --> 00:07:58.750
Who are you?

00:07:59.830 --> 00:08:01.030
Pass a message to her?

00:08:03.560 --> 00:08:04.240
Oh my.

00:08:04.720 --> 00:08:05.320
Wang Fang!

00:08:05.510 --> 00:08:06.120
Wang Fang!

00:08:08.920 --> 00:08:10.380
It's Yuanji's fan, right?

00:08:10.870 --> 00:08:12.800
What message did they want to pass?

00:08:13.190 --> 00:08:14.070
It's too mean.

00:08:14.070 --> 00:08:15.000
I can't say it.

00:08:16.510 --> 00:08:17.110
Wang Fang,

00:08:17.360 --> 00:08:19.120
you have to be careful these days.

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:20.720
These fans are crazy.

00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:21.310
Yeah.

00:08:21.430 --> 00:08:22.510
They must have doxxed you.

00:08:22.510 --> 00:08:24.000
They even called here.

00:08:24.070 --> 00:08:24.750
Maybe

00:08:24.830 --> 00:08:26.270
they've found your address.

00:08:26.270 --> 00:08:27.750
You must be careful.

00:08:27.800 --> 00:08:28.390
Be careful.

00:08:28.390 --> 00:08:29.750
Those fans are so crazy.

00:08:29.750 --> 00:08:30.810
It's so dangerous.

00:08:31.120 --> 00:08:32.150
How about asking a male colleague

00:08:32.150 --> 00:08:33.679
-to escort you home?
-Yeah.

00:08:35.030 --> 00:08:35.720
If anyone

00:08:36.120 --> 00:08:37.510
gets a call for Wang Fang,

00:08:37.510 --> 00:08:38.870
just say there's no such person
in the company.

00:08:38.870 --> 00:08:39.669
Understood?

00:08:40.840 --> 00:08:42.360
Understood.

00:08:42.720 --> 00:08:43.320
Wang Fang.

00:08:44.200 --> 00:08:44.930
Come with me.

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:49.960
Director,

00:08:50.670 --> 00:08:51.270
I'm sorry!

00:08:52.120 --> 00:08:52.790
Have a seat.

00:08:55.320 --> 00:08:56.720
I don't mean to blame you.

00:08:57.270 --> 00:08:58.270
I just think

00:08:58.750 --> 00:08:59.750
what you did

00:09:00.670 --> 00:09:01.870
was a bit irrational.

00:09:02.750 --> 00:09:03.870
I was so sad.

00:09:04.360 --> 00:09:05.200
I didn't want Yuanji

00:09:05.200 --> 00:09:06.750
to disappear from my life.

00:09:07.670 --> 00:09:09.320
It's bad enough he disappeared,

00:09:09.320 --> 00:09:11.480
but he even became an idol.

00:09:12.120 --> 00:09:13.080
Every day when I scroll on my phone,

00:09:13.080 --> 00:09:13.840
I see him.

00:09:13.840 --> 00:09:15.320
Who could stand that?

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:17.000
I understand you.

00:09:17.320 --> 00:09:18.270
My concern is

00:09:18.510 --> 00:09:19.870
that Yuanji's fans

00:09:19.960 --> 00:09:20.870
are quite young

00:09:21.240 --> 00:09:22.100
and impulsive.

00:09:22.510 --> 00:09:24.370
I'm afraid they might harass you.

00:09:25.750 --> 00:09:27.280
Have they been calling you?

00:09:27.320 --> 00:09:29.720
I don't answer calls from unknown numbers.

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:33.960
I think

00:09:35.480 --> 00:09:37.140
you should take a few days off.

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:38.390
Are you firing me?

00:09:38.910 --> 00:09:39.790
No.

00:09:40.200 --> 00:09:41.260
With my authority,

00:09:41.390 --> 00:09:42.990
I can only give you 3 days off.

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:44.270
Add your annual leave to it,

00:09:44.270 --> 00:09:45.960
and you can go out to relax.

00:09:46.390 --> 00:09:47.590
Thank you, Director.

00:09:49.670 --> 00:09:51.270
I can work!

00:09:51.750 --> 00:09:52.790
Go out for a bit.

00:09:53.270 --> 00:09:55.030
Maybe you'll meet a better man.

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:56.120
Even if you don't,

00:09:56.270 --> 00:09:57.360
a change of scenery

00:09:57.600 --> 00:09:58.930
might change your mood.

00:10:00.510 --> 00:10:02.110
Actually, I don't regret it.

00:10:04.550 --> 00:10:05.440
I just want

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:06.720
the world to see

00:10:08.150 --> 00:10:10.510
how close we used to be.

00:10:26.780 --> 00:10:28.640
Can I get some more water, please?

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:34.870
For taking up public resources,

00:10:34.870 --> 00:10:35.730
I am very sorry.

00:10:36.390 --> 00:10:36.840
Today,

00:10:37.200 --> 00:10:38.750
I must give everyone an explanation.

00:10:38.750 --> 00:10:39.750
As everyone knows,

00:10:39.750 --> 00:10:41.120
I am not a real human

00:10:41.670 --> 00:10:43.400
and do not have physical needs.

00:10:43.790 --> 00:10:44.990
All the leaked images

00:10:45.480 --> 00:10:46.480
are AI-edited.

00:10:47.000 --> 00:10:47.730
I personally

00:10:48.150 --> 00:10:50.080
do not know the woman in the photos.

00:10:50.750 --> 00:10:51.550
If necessary,

00:10:52.150 --> 00:10:53.680
legal action will be taken.

00:10:54.910 --> 00:10:57.360
Filthy woman! Ultimate delusional fangirl!

00:10:57.360 --> 00:10:59.200
A disgrace to women! Shameless!

00:10:59.390 --> 00:11:00.320
She should be erased

00:11:00.320 --> 00:11:01.450
from the beginning!

00:11:01.960 --> 00:11:02.890
It really is her!

00:11:05.200 --> 00:11:06.000
It really is her!

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:06.670
It's her!

00:11:06.690 --> 00:11:07.660
It really is!

00:11:12.240 --> 00:11:12.910
Hello?

00:11:13.750 --> 00:11:14.350
Is this Ya?

00:11:14.910 --> 00:11:16.710
Are you Wang Fang's supervisor?

00:11:17.240 --> 00:11:17.960
Who is this?

00:11:18.480 --> 00:11:19.200
I'm asking if you are

00:11:19.200 --> 00:11:20.200
Wang Fang's supervisor.

00:11:20.200 --> 00:11:21.510
I am Wang Fang's supervisor.

00:11:21.510 --> 00:11:22.770
What's wrong with her?

00:11:22.840 --> 00:11:23.670
I'm from a debt collection agency

00:11:23.670 --> 00:11:24.870
hired by the platform.

00:11:24.870 --> 00:11:26.120
We've lost contact with Wang Fang.

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:27.320
If she keeps this up,

00:11:27.630 --> 00:11:30.230
we'll come to your company
to collect the debt!

00:11:30.840 --> 00:11:32.500
You'd better watch your tone.

00:11:32.600 --> 00:11:33.720
I don't know about this,

00:11:33.720 --> 00:11:35.030
but harassing her contacts

00:11:35.030 --> 00:11:35.870
is illegal.

00:11:36.750 --> 00:11:37.960
Debts must be paid.

00:11:38.630 --> 00:11:40.090
We can't reach the debtor.

00:11:40.200 --> 00:11:41.440
She owes money and disappeared.

00:11:41.440 --> 00:11:43.000
We are just following the rules.

00:11:43.000 --> 00:11:44.200
How much does she owe?

00:11:44.440 --> 00:11:45.670
The amount assigned to us

00:11:45.670 --> 00:11:47.030
is around 200,000.

00:11:47.640 --> 00:11:48.550
With other platforms,

00:11:48.550 --> 00:11:49.200
in total,

00:11:49.480 --> 00:11:50.720
I estimate it's between 600,000

00:11:50.720 --> 00:11:51.480
to 800,000.

00:11:51.840 --> 00:11:52.790
I don't know the exact figure.

00:11:52.790 --> 00:11:54.720
What did she need so much money for?

00:11:55.120 --> 00:11:57.030
We can see her transaction records.

00:11:57.030 --> 00:11:58.320
It was all spent on games.

00:11:58.320 --> 00:12:00.000
Those dating simulator games.

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:01.750
She even spent money
to push a game character

00:12:01.750 --> 00:12:02.880
to be the top seller.

00:12:08.110 --> 00:12:09.630
Wang Fang, pay your debts!

00:12:09.910 --> 00:12:11.000
You awful woman!

00:12:11.270 --> 00:12:13.510
Pay your debts. Shameless!

00:12:16.320 --> 00:12:17.650
You slandered someone!

00:12:17.780 --> 00:12:19.240
Wang Fang, you vile woman.

00:12:20.360 --> 00:12:21.750
You are so vicious.

00:12:22.390 --> 00:12:24.120
I'm going to expose you online.

00:12:24.390 --> 00:12:25.720
If you keep this up,

00:12:25.750 --> 00:12:27.030
you'll get hit by a car!

00:12:32.260 --> 00:12:34.060
Sorry, the number you dialed...

00:12:38.120 --> 00:12:38.720
Come out!

00:12:38.840 --> 00:12:40.100
Why won't you come out?

00:12:40.150 --> 00:12:40.870
Why are you hiding inside the room?

00:12:40.870 --> 00:12:42.240
This won't solve the problem!

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:43.500
Stop hiding! Come out!

00:12:44.000 --> 00:12:44.730
Come out now!

00:12:45.150 --> 00:12:46.390
What's the use of hiding?

00:12:46.390 --> 00:12:47.050
Seriously.

00:12:47.080 --> 00:12:47.720
Is it her?

00:12:48.000 --> 00:12:48.750
No.

00:12:48.870 --> 00:12:49.930
It's not this girl.

00:12:50.080 --> 00:12:51.390
I'm her supervisor.

00:12:52.030 --> 00:12:52.960
Does she gamble?

00:12:52.960 --> 00:12:54.080
You're her supervisor?

00:12:54.080 --> 00:12:55.000
This is too dangerous.

00:12:55.000 --> 00:12:55.930
We all live here.

00:12:56.000 --> 00:12:57.030
What is she doing?

00:12:57.080 --> 00:12:58.340
You have to let us know.

00:12:58.360 --> 00:12:59.150
Yeah.

00:12:59.360 --> 00:13:00.200
You have to let us know.

00:13:00.200 --> 00:13:01.400
This is so dangerous.

00:13:03.390 --> 00:13:04.270
What the hell is this?

00:13:04.270 --> 00:13:05.240
We all have kids.

00:13:05.320 --> 00:13:06.840
That's right.

00:13:08.130 --> 00:13:08.790
It's her!

00:13:09.240 --> 00:13:09.790
It's her!

00:13:10.390 --> 00:13:11.150
Wang Fang?

00:13:12.360 --> 00:13:13.030
Director!

00:13:13.270 --> 00:13:14.080
I'm sorry!

00:13:15.360 --> 00:13:16.390
Don't go!

00:13:16.550 --> 00:13:18.150
Don't go! Don't go!

00:13:18.960 --> 00:13:22.320
Come out! Come out!

00:14:31.200 --> 00:14:32.400
All the leaked images

00:14:32.600 --> 00:14:33.630
are AI-edited.

00:14:34.120 --> 00:14:34.850
I personally

00:14:35.320 --> 00:14:37.250
do not know the woman in the photos.

00:14:38.440 --> 00:14:39.380
You slandered someone!

00:14:39.380 --> 00:14:40.360
Pay your debts.

00:14:40.360 --> 00:14:41.480
I will expose you on the Internet!

00:14:41.480 --> 00:14:43.120
Pay your debts! Shameless!

00:14:43.390 --> 00:14:44.650
You will be hit by a car!

00:14:46.200 --> 00:14:47.510
Goodbye,

00:14:47.790 --> 00:14:49.000
Yuanji!

00:14:52.270 --> 00:14:53.120
Yuhuang...

00:14:54.670 --> 00:14:56.550
It is already past midnight.

00:14:59.600 --> 00:15:01.510
Have you forgotten me too?

00:15:14.720 --> 00:15:15.360
Yuhuang!

00:15:19.440 --> 00:15:20.240
Shouldn't you

00:15:20.240 --> 00:15:21.500
have forgotten me too?

00:15:24.880 --> 00:15:26.830
I have no money left!

00:15:29.240 --> 00:15:29.840
Come on!

00:15:30.360 --> 00:15:31.120
Don't be afraid!